            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "FYI, you ~~are~~were running the dev server in debug mode with evalex enabled. Also, you are running it with root permissions. This means that **ANYONE was able to execute command as root on your machine!**\n\nI used the [werkzeug debugger shell](http://www.holmusk.com/console) to kill the dev server to remove the risk a compromised machine poses to the internet (black hats tend to abuse them for attacks, bitcoin mining, spam, warez, and other unwanted things).\n\nHowever, since it's impossible to know for sure if someone else also found out about it, you should assume the machine has already been compromised and reinstall it from scratch!\n"
